# RELEASE — zsh-snap-list

Version:  v2.0
Date:     2026-04-06
Platform: openSUSE Tumbleweed
Shell:    zsh 5.9+

---

## What's in this release

### v2.0 — Interactive menu + combinable flags
- Interactive 3-step menu: config (root/home/all), filter (none/important/single/pre_post), quantity (all/last N)
- Equivalent command displayed after menu — teaches flags naturally
- Flags: `-a` `-c` `-i` `-t` `-n` `-h` — fully combinable
- Empty result guard with clear message
- Summary line adapts to filtered result

### v1.0 — Initial release
- Colorized output: green (active), yellow (important=yes), bold (headers)
- Summary line: total, singles, pre, post, importants count
